HOTFIX BRANCH:
If there are any urgent fixes from production we create hotfix branch from main. 
You create a hotfix branch from the main/production branch (often called main or master)
Make the necessary fix
Test it quickly
Merge it back into:
the production branch (to deploy immediately) and usually to the development branch (so the fix isn’t lost in future releases).
